remarks: Membership in a left closed, right open interval.  (Contributed by Glauco Siliprandi, 11-Dec-2019.)
statement:
elicod.a $e |- ( ph -> A e. RR* ) $.
elicod.b $e |- ( ph -> B e. RR* ) $.
elicod.3 $e |- ( ph -> C e. RR* ) $.
elicod.4 $e |- ( ph -> A <_ C ) $.
elicod.5 $e |- ( ph -> C < B ) $.
elicod $p |- ( ph -> C e. ( A [,) B ) ) $.
